#### [NEW] `app/api/company/route.ts`

**Endpoint**: `GET /api/company?symbol=FPT`

**TCBS API calls (song song)**:
```typescript
const [reportRes, ratingRes, overviewRes] = await Promise.all([
  // 4 năm financial report
  fetch(`https://apipubaws.tcbs.com.vn/tcanalysis/v1/finance/${symbol}/financialreport?yearly=4&quarterly=0`),
  // Rating
  fetch(`https://apipubaws.tcbs.com.vn/tcanalysis/v1/rating/${symbol}/rating`),
  // Overview (đã dùng trong quote)
  fetch(`https://apipubaws.tcbs.com.vn/stock-insight/v1/stock/ticker-overview?ticker=${symbol}`)
])
```

**Parse logic cho yearly array**:
```typescript
// TCBS trả về array 4 phần tử, mỗi phần tử 1 năm (mới → cũ)
const reports = await reportRes.json() // Array<{...}>
const yearly = reports.map((r, i) => ({
  year: new Date().getFullYear() - i,
  revenue: (r.revenue || 0) / 1e9,              // → tỷ VNĐ
  netIncome: (r.netIncome || r.postTaxProfit || 0) / 1e9,
  eps: (r.eps || 0) * 1000,                      // → VNĐ
  roe: (r.roe || 0) * 100,                       // → %
  roa: (r.roa || 0) * 100,
  debtEquity: r.debtOnEquity || 0,
  pe: r.pe || 0,
  pb: r.pb || 0,
  dividendYield: (r.dividendYield || 0) * 100,
  revenueGrowth: (r.revenueGrowth || 0) * 100,
  profitGrowth: (r.earningGrowth || 0) * 100,
}))
```

**Response type**: `CompanyData` (xem Types bên dưới)  
**Cache**: `revalidate = 3600` (1 giờ)

